OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FKing's former school bans  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fuse of mobile phones       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Scottish boarding school once        
OL,6, attended by King Charles III has banned
OL,7, the use of mobile phones within the    
OL,8, school.                                
OL,10,FPupils at Gordonstoun are expected to  
OL,11,Fleave their phones in their boarding   
OL,12,Fhouses during the day as well as       
OL,13,Fhanding them into staff overnight.     
OL,15,FThe school said it was concerned about 
OL,16,Fthe "addictive" nature of mobiles.     
OL,18,FThe new policy extends previous limits 
OL,19,Fon phone use which are said to have    
OL,20,Fboosted exam results.                  
